   Laverty
OMNÍPOTENS sempitérne Deus, qui in Corde beátæ Maríæ Vírginis dignum Spíritus Sancti habitáculum præparásti: concéde propítius; ut ejúsdem immaculáti Cordis festivitátem devóta mente recoléntes, secúndum Cor tuum vívere valeámus. Per Dóminum... in unitáte ejúsdem Spíritus Sancti.
ALMIGHTY everlasting God, who in the Heart of the blessed Virgin Mary didst prepare a dwelling worthy of the Holy Ghost: grant in thy mercy, that we who with devout minds celebrate the festival of that immacuate Heart, may be able to live according to thine own Heart. Through our Lord...in the unity of the same Holy Spirit.
